prompt_text: Describe the scene of a flood.
content_text: In 2013, the Cosa ha damn just broke down in my village, Bihar and all of my relative they were living there. I came to United. Flood is going on there. We were not able to talk to them. There was no food, there was no shelter for them. They were living on a mountain because backside of my home there are mountain. They were living at that, no connectivity. We were trying to connect with them, no data, anything. Now we can use WhatsApp, but at that point of time that was not there. So we were unable to contact with them or. The situation was worst. They have to travel via boat to reach at the safest place so that they can survive.
